Get Ready With Me!

Dive into my daily skincare & makeup routine.

One of the most important parts of my makeup routine is taking care of and prepping my skin! 

Uncared for skin could be the cause for breakage in foundation, patchy coverage and rough texture that fades away faster. 

Thankfully with @biobeautylab I’m able to make sure my skin stays healthy and looks good with or without makeup! 

✨🤍✨

Clear, smooth & glowing skin with @biobeautylab 🦋✨

Products used:

Potent-C Power Serum // Use twice daily to maintain an even skin tone, get rid of darkspots, and improve the look of fine lines & wrinkles.

Gentle Retinol & Peptide Serum // Use once every 3 days to even out skin texture, minimize your pores and maintain your skin’s moisture!
